#: ../../source/strategy.md:1
msgid "Strategic Hub (Obsidian)"
msgstr "戦略ハブ (Obsidian)"

#: ../../source/strategy.md:3
msgid ""
"The Strategic Hub is the heart of the Spec-Craft workflow. It leverages "
"Obsidian to maintain a high-level creative roadmap that guides all "
"implementation efforts."
msgstr ""
"戦略ハブは、Spec-"
"Craftワークフローの心臓部です。Obsidianを活用して、すべての実装作業を導くハイレベルなクリエイティブロードマップを維持します。"

#: ../../source/strategy.md:5
msgid "Strategy vs Tactics Analogy"
msgstr "戦略 vs 戦術の比喩"

#: ../../source/strategy.md:6
msgid ""
"Understanding the difference between strategy and tactics is key to the "
"Spec-Craft philosophy:"
msgstr "戦略と戦術の違いを理解することは、Spec-Craftの哲学において重要です："

