#: ../../source/strategy.md:17
msgid "The Bridge"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/strategy.md:18
msgid ""
"Spec-Craft acts as the bridge, allowing AI agents to read the strategy in"
" Obsidian and translate it into tactical tasks in spec-kit."
msgstr ""

